  "aideTuto1Q": "How do I light a firefly?",
  "@aideTuto1Q": { "description": "Tutorial 1: question" },
  "aideTuto1R": "Go to the \"Write\" tab, note a positive thing you observed in your neighbourhood, then tap \"Light a firefly\". You can add a location and a photo.",
  "@aideTuto1R": { "description": "Tutorial 1: answer" },
  "aideTuto2Q": "How do I add a location to an entry?",
  "@aideTuto2Q": { "description": "Tutorial 2: question" },
  "aideTuto2R": "In the entry form, tap the \"Location\" field. You can use your GPS position or type a name manually.",
  "@aideTuto2R": { "description": "Tutorial 2: answer" },
  "aideTuto3Q": "How do I find my fireflies again?",
  "@aideTuto3Q": { "description": "Tutorial 3: question" },
  "aideTuto3R": "Your fireflies appear in the \"Map\" tab (on the map) and in the \"Me\" tab (timeline). Only fireflies with a location show on the map.",
  "@aideTuto3R": { "description": "Tutorial 3: answer" },
  "aideTuto4Q": "How do I filter by season?",
  "@aideTuto4Q": { "description": "Tutorial 4: question" },
  "aideTuto4R": "In the \"Me\" tab, use the season filters (Spring, Summer, Autumn, Winter) just above your timeline.",
  "@aideTuto4R": { "description": "Tutorial 4: answer" },
  "aideFaq1Q": "Can I delete a firefly?",
  "@aideFaq1Q": { "description": "FAQ 1: question" },
  "aideFaq1R": "Yes. In your timeline (\"Me\" tab), swipe an entry to the left to reveal the delete button. This action is irreversible.",
  "@aideFaq1R": { "description": "FAQ 1: answer" },
  "aideFaq2Q": "Is my data private?",
  "@aideFaq2Q": { "description": "FAQ 2: question" },
  "aideFaq2R": "Entries with a location may appear on the community map. Without a location, they remain invisible to others. You can also filter the display from the map.",
  "@aideFaq2R": { "description": "FAQ 2: answer" },
  "aideFaq3Q": "Can I use the app without an account?",
  "@aideFaq3Q": { "description": "FAQ 3: question" },
  "aideFaq3R": "You can explore the community map without an account. To light fireflies and retrieve your memories, you will need to create a free account.",
  "@aideFaq3R": { "description": "FAQ 3: answer" },
  "aideFaq4Q": "How does moderation work?",
  "@aideFaq4Q": { "description": "FAQ 4: question" },
  "aideFaq4R": "Lucioles is built on kindness. Any reported content is reviewed by our team. Inappropriate content is hidden to preserve a positive and respectful space.",
  "@aideFaq4R": { "description": "FAQ 4: answer" },

